  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You infuse spells with heavenly power, drastically increasing their effectiveness against would-be heralds of evil.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Aasimar, able to prepare or cast consecrate.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>A consecrated spell is treated as a maximized spell against evil creatures and creatures with the evil subtype. Against all other creatures, this feat does not modify the spell in any way (for example, a consecrated fireball acts as a normal fireball against neutral or good creatures). This feat does not stack with Maximize Spell. A consecrated spell uses up a spell slot two levels higher than the spell's actual level.",
